  <brief_title>Safety and Efficacy Study of Pain Shield Device to Treat Subjects Following Laparoscopic-Assisted Abdominal Surgery</brief_title>
  <official_title>Evaluation of Safety and Efficacy of the PainShield Device for the Treatment of Subjects Who Underwent Laparoscopic-Assisted Abdominal Surgery</official_title>
