  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate safety and efficacy of PainShield device, based on
      ultrasound technology, for postoperative pain relief and wound healing following a
      laparoscopic-assisted abdominal surgery.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
